ost-image" alt="马克·莱根。图片来源：史蒂夫·古利克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Mark-Lanegan.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Depeche-Mode">Depeche Mode</a>的 Dave Gahan、 <a href="/artists/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>的<a href="/artists/Josh-Homme">Josh Homme</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Chrissie-Hynde">Chrissie Hynde</a>等人已被宣布为今年冬天向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-lanegan">Mark Lanegan</a>致敬的演出的表演者。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/mark-lanegan-obituary-tribute-3167245">Mark Lanegan，1964 – 2022：现代另类摇滚的基石</a></strong></li></ul><p>这场名为“Mark Lanegan – 一场庆典”的演出将纪念这位已故歌手兼词曲作家，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/mark-lanegan-has-died-aged-57-3167192">于 2022 年初去世，享年 57 岁</a>。演唱会将于 12 月 5 日在伦敦 Roundhouse 举行，这将是他的 60 岁生日，也是他在伦敦最后一次现场亮相的地方。</p><p>其他准备在演出中表演的音乐家包括<a href="/artists/Primal-Scream">Primal Scream</a>的<a href="/artists/Bobby-Gillespie">Bobby Gillespie</a> 、Greg Dulli、 <a href="/artists/The-Kills">The Kills</a>的<a href="/artists/Alison-Mosshart">Alison Mosshart</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Soulsavers">Soulsavers</a>等。一般门票销售将于当地时间周二（10 月 1 日）上午 10 点开始。<a href="https://myticket.co.uk/artists/lanegan-60" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797029" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797029" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy"