知道如何玩行业游戏，并通过太直率或诚实来弄乱了很多机会”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="与急救套件和&#39;euphoria&#39;一起使用“污垢femme” |在谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Wo6pyHDKPDQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Tove Lo最近的专辑是2022年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tove-lo-dirt-femme-review-3326558#:~:text=The%20result%20is%20an%20album,a%20slave%20to%20the%20algorithm.">“ Dirt Femme”</a> （她作为独立艺术家的第一张），该专辑被<em>NME</em>授予四星级。该评论将记录描述为“刺耳的，令人惊讶的，不太凝聚，但从未无聊。 Tove Lo总是很有趣，无法成为算法的奴隶。”</p><p>今年，她还与紧密的合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sg-lewis">SG Lewis</a>放弃了“热” EP， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tove-lo-sg-lewis-interview-heat-ep-queer-lgbtq-sex-club-3765871">并告诉<em>NME</em>是为“为酷儿舞池”的</a>。</p><p>在夏天，她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">凯莉·米洛（Kylie Minogue）的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-shares-dance-y-new-single-my-oh-my-with-bebe-rexha-and-tove-lo-3773886">单曲“ My Oh My My”</a>上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Bebe-Rexha">Bebe Rexha</a>一起出演，Pop Trio于7月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST Hyde Park</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kylie-minogue-give-my-oh-my-its-live-debut-with-bebe-rexha-and-tove-lo-3775089">现场亮相</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tove-lo-looks-back-on-10-years-of-queen-of-the-clouds-i-was-such-a-mess-when-i-wrote-these-songs-but-i-still-feel-100-per-cent-that-this-album-is-me-today-3797018">Tove Lo回顾了10年的“乌云皇后”：“当我写这些歌曲时，我真是一团糟，但我仍然觉得100％的专辑是这张专辑今天是我的”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
